    "description": {
        "en-US": "Special send button is placed on original send button position (replaced!) and add a feature to confirm domain which is treated by \"internals\".\nNote that original send button is moved to right side of toolbar  in mail compose window.\n\nHow to setup after installing this addon:\n\n1. Open Config Editor\n2. Set <code>extensions.send-to-internals@clear-code.com.domains</code> to \"LIST OF TARGET DOMAINS\".\n\nThe list of target domains are treated as check list when sending E-mail to different domains. It must be space separated such as \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/2141eac2eacda036b00afc30fd0a7e6f24e9bddf402cf4393fe5144f468147e8/http%3A//example.com\">example.com</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/0c6b88b70003219bf04c0f69986472bf7f1bfa53fb842927b8b3025c0284915f/http%3A//example.jp\">example.jp</a>\" and so on.",
        "ja": "既定の送信ボタンの代わりに社内へ送信ボタンが追加されます。(既定の送信ボタンは社外へ送信)\n\nアドオンインストール後の設定方法:\n\n1. 設定エディタを開く\n2.  <code>extensions.send-to-internals@clear-code.com.domains</code>に社内とみなすドメインのリストを設定する。\n\n社内送信時の送信先のドメインが異なる場合に警告します。複数のドメインを指定する場合はスペース区切りで指定します。"
    },
